data.description: A treasure uncovered in a secluded, local traffic only, pedestrian friendly part of North Port. This worry-free split plan home sports a new roof (2022) and a newly updated kitchen with granite countertops wood cabinets, eat up bar, laundry room with all appliances approximately 3 years old - including the air conditioner and hot water heater. The front yard has been lovingly restored with new sod and plantings and offers a new paver walkway leading to the front entrance. There you will find the entrance door has glass insets and all Palladium windows showering your home with lots of light. Inside the living room is warm and inviting, offering a great place to relax or enter the lanai and pool area through sliders. The dining room and dinette are adjacent to the kitchen and offer sliders to the pool area, as well. Adjacent to the pool area is the 2nd bath allowing bathers ease of access to the house after enjoying their swim. This split plan home offers 2 bedrooms which share the pool bath and features a tub and shower combination. Outside there are new pavers surrounding the inviting pool offering a private and relaxing outdoor space. This home has tile throughout except for two carpeted bedrooms and vinyl plank flooring in the 3rd bedroom; the master has newly installed carpet and offers sliders to the pool area. Two oversized closets are adjacent to the master bath which features dual sinks and a walk-in shower. Two of the 3 bedrooms are supersized and boast oversize closets. A whole-house RO system has been installed. Outside and in the back of the home is a separate storage room, perfect for a handyman’s tool collection or storage for all your Halloween and/or Christmas decorations. Purchase this home with existing furniture for yourself or as a rental. What are you waiting for; make this one yours before someone else beats you to it.
